short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays all ratemyprofessor.com ratings when seaching for classes on beartracks.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When viewing classes on Beartracks the professors name is highlighted with a color corresponding to their rateMyProfessor score. 

Simply hover over their name to view more insights.

Rate my Professor for Beartracks is unaffiliated with the University of Alberta or RateMyProfessor.com
